    "The next layer is of size 6 × 6 × 256.",
    "Here 6 × 6 × 256 means 9216 neurons.",
    "Number of layers are 256 and each layer have 36 neurons in it.",
    "• For dense connection, they employ fully connect each 9216 neurons to first hidden layer having 4096 neurons which have 4096 × 9216 connections.",
    "• These 4096 neurons are fully connected to the next hidden layer having 4096 neurons size of 4096 × 4096 connections.• Finally the output layer will be of 1000 neurons which is fully connected to the previous layer size of 1000 × 9216 connections."
